  "keyFeatures": [
    "AI-powered bot builder with natural language instructions",
    "Visual WhatsApp Flow builder with drag-and-drop screens",
    "Built-in per-project database with schema management",
    "Conversation and contact management dashboard",
    "WhatsApp Business API integration via Meta embedded signup",
    "Message template creation and management",
    "Secrets manager for API keys and credentials",
    "Execution logs and real-time debugging",
    "Version history with commit restore",
    "Live testing via Paige Dev phone link",
    "Team workspaces with role-based access",
    "Subscription billing with credits system"
